OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry morning with sunny
OL,6,Fspells. Some bright or sunny intervals
OL,7,Fin the afternoon but generally
OL,8,Fcloudier with the odd shower possible.
OL,9,FMostly light winds but breezy around
OL,10,Fthe coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA mostly cloudy evening with
OL,13,Fa few showers possible, dry with clear
OL,14,Fspells however over Moray. Remaining
OL,15,Fcloudy overnight with showers possible
OL,16,Ffor all parts. Light northwesterly
OL,17,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
