OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA cloudy and overcast day with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of showery rain spreading
OL,7,Fsouthwards. Showers may become heavy
OL,8,Fat times in the afternoon.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FHigh
OL,11,Fpressure dominates bringing a dry and
OL,12,Fsettled few days with light winds.
OL,13,FPlenty of bright and sunny spells, but
OL,14,Foften cloudier near the coast.
